<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home | Medical Schemes Portal</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: #f8fafc;
            margin: 0;
        }

        header {
            background: #0077b6;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 0;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        nav {
            width: 90%;
            margin: auto;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        nav h2 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 1.6em;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: #caf0f8;
        }

        .container {
            width: 90%;
            margin: 50px auto;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #023e8a;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            color: #333;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 25px;
            background: #0077b6;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: #0096c7;
        }

        footer {
            background: #0077b6;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav>
            <h2>Medical Schemes Portal</h2>
            <div class="nav-links">
                <a href="/">Home</a>
                <a href="/about">About Us</a>
                <a href="/contact">Contact Us</a>
                <a href="/schemes">Schemes</a>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to the Medical Schemes Portal</h1>
        <p>Explore various government and private healthcare schemes designed to support citizens with medical and financial assistance.</p>
        <a class="btn" href="/schemes">View All Schemes</a>
    </div>

    <footer>
        &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Medical Schemes Portal | All Rights Reserved
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
